WEBVTT

00:00.477 --> 00:02.979
<i>Previously on The Secret Life of</i>
<i>the American Teenager...</i>

00:02.981 --> 00:04.882
I'm getting our things
ready for the hospital.

00:04.916 --> 00:06.283
Do you think that this...

00:07.585 --> 00:08.719
This could be it?

00:08.753 --> 00:10.053
Could be.

00:10.088 --> 00:12.589
Everything about Africa,
it just makes me feel so alive.

00:12.624 --> 00:14.391
That's why I want
to go back, Kathleen.

00:14.425 --> 00:15.826
Obviously I want you
to come with me.

00:15.860 --> 00:17.394
Tom and Grace can come too.

00:17.428 --> 00:19.463
I mean, that's an amazing opportunity
for them to see the world.

00:19.497 --> 00:20.831
Did you feel
the baby move?

00:20.865 --> 00:23.967
No. But I'm thinking maybe she's
just getting into position

00:24.002 --> 00:25.636
to, you know,
make her way out.

00:25.670 --> 00:27.070
Let's see
what's going on.

00:29.073 --> 00:30.507
You tested out
of high school?

00:30.542 --> 00:32.543
We were thinking about
driving across America.

00:32.577 --> 00:33.877
That was Ben.

00:33.912 --> 00:35.112
Is everything okay?

00:35.146 --> 00:36.613
No, everything's
not okay.

00:36.648 --> 00:39.516
I'll call you as soon as I know
how serious this is, all right?

00:40.852 --> 00:42.386
I love you, Leo.

00:42.420 --> 00:44.521
<i>Who is this woman with two</i>
<i>children that wants to marry Tom?</i>

00:44.556 --> 00:46.156
I mean, is she after
his money or something?

00:46.191 --> 00:47.424
I don't want
to be in a situation

00:47.458 --> 00:48.892
where I'm forced
to run away from home.

00:48.927 --> 00:50.427
Let me do
what I wanna do.

00:50.461 --> 00:52.563
I've got some bad
news for all of you.

00:52.597 --> 00:54.231
The baby passed away.

00:54.256 --> 00:57.756
